MID_支援_カミラ_ハロルド_Ｃ: $a$t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|Sigh...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Lady Camilla... is there\nsomething on your mind?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaI'm surprised you noticed.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaSo I was right!$k$pI am a man who jumps into\naction whenever I hear a sigh.$k$p$E通常,|So, what could be troubling you?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaIt's about $Nu...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,汗|$Nu...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Yes. My entire being is filled\nwith love for $Nu.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|Indeed. That is a well-known fact\nin some sections of the kingdom.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|But, I don't think my feelings are going\nthrough... It makes me so sad...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaIs that how it is?$k$p$Eキメ,|Then, if there is any way I can help you,\njust give me the word.$k$pI shall ensure that your feelings are\nfaithfully transmitted to $Nu.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Very well. I would be pleased if\nyou could tell $Nu how I feel.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Consider it done, milady.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|However, this is a delicate matter. Be sure\nto watch your words and actions carefully.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Understood.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Let's see then... What I\nwanted to tell $Nu is...$k
MID_支援_カミラ_ハロルド_Ｂ: $a$t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaLady Camilla, please, excuse my delayed\nreturn. I have completed your task.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|And what did $Nu say?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|It's just, um...\nThe results were unfavorable...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Huh?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|First, please allow me to\nexplain how it all happened.$k$pI thought that such a delicate topic would\nhave been ill-suited for the busy evenings...$k$pSo I spoke with $Nu\nbefore they retired for bed.$k$p$Eキメ,|Of course, I had spoken with $Nu\nabout this matter through the wall.$k$pSo as not to disturb their\nslumber at this late hour.$k$p$E笑,|With regards to this,\nyou should not worry yourself.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|A-all right...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaAs you instructed, I delivered $Nu\nthe message of your fervent love.$k$pThen, from across the wall, $Nu\nreplied with just one sentence.$k$p$E苦,|What they said was,\n"Please, stop this."$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,汗|N-no!$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaDo not cry, Lady Camilla...$k$p$E怒,汗|I'm positive that $Nu has their own\ncircumstances to take into consideration.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa…………$k$p$E怒,|...Wait a moment. Last night, the royal\nfamily's sleeping quarters were moved.$k$pYou said you never saw $Nu's\nface during this exchange, but... $k$p$E怒,汗|You did take the move into account,\nright...?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|...This is my first time ever\nof such an arrangement.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Then did you perhaps speak\nto someone who wasn't $Nu?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa...I will not rule out the possibility.$k$pNow that you mention it, before I relayed\nyour words of love, I did hear something.$k$pAs if someone were singing\nfrom inside the room...$k$pIf that was not a hallucination, then...$k$pI may have been speaking to Lady Aqua...$k$p$E怒,汗|By the gods,\nwhat a grave error I've made!$k$pYou have my deepest apologies. I simply\nwished to assist you in any way I could...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|It's all right...\nEveryone makes mistakes...$k$pAnd rather than a mistake,\nthis was simply bad luck on your part.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|You are too kind, milady...$k$pIf I may impose, please, give me\nanother chance. I shall not fail you again.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|All right.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Thank you. I, Harold, shall\nstake my honor upon this task.$k
MID_支援_カミラ_ハロルド_Ａ: $a$t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$w0|Lady Camilla, please excuse my delayed\nreturn. I have completed your task.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|How did it go? Tell me.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Nu and Lady Aqua just so\nhappened to be together when I went.$k$p$Eキメ,|I asked Lady Aqua to ignore\nyour professed love to her...$k$pAnd, although she simply tilted her\nhead in response to my request...$k$pI do believe she understood.$k$p$E笑,|I delivered to $Nu the message of\nyour profound love, as you've instructed.$k$p$E苦,|And then $Nu said again,\n"Please stop this."$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|Huh...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaIt pained me so to think your\nfeelings could be unrequited...$k$p$E怒,汗|So much, that I fled the scene,\nclutching my dizzied head.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Huh? Why did you feel dizzy?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|Oh, that?$k$pWhile I was heading to $Nu's\nquarters, I was struck twice by horse carts.$k$pIt was then that I must have injured\nmy head. It left me rather light-headed.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Oh, is that what happened?$k$pI just spoke with $Nu,\nbut nothing was making sense to me.$k$pNow, I understand after\nhearing what you've told me.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|Huh? What do you mean, Lady Camilla?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|You were dizzy after hitting your head...$k$pAnd that caused you to mistake\n$Nu for Aqua,$k$pand Aqua for $Nu.$k$p$E通常,|Perhaps that is what happened.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Th-that explains everything!$k$p$E怒,汗|No, this is no time to rejoice!$k$pPlease, have mercy upon me!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Oh, I don't mind.\nIt was just bad luck on your part again.$k$pPeople do say you have the\nworst luck in all of Nohr.$k$pYou did well while working\nagainst such a handicap.$k$pIt doesn't seem to have hurt\nmy relationship with $Nu anyway.$k$p$E笑,|I know you were only trying to help,\nand you did try so hard.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|Lady Camilla... Once again, you show\nme more kindness than I deserve...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Oh, I'm not worried about that.$k$pPeople are rarely able to communicate\ntheir feelings to one another.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Milady, if you would, please...$k$pGrace your faithful servant\nHarold with one more chance!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|N-no, I think I'll pass.$k
MID_支援_カミラ_ハロルド_Ｓ: $a$t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaLady Camilla...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaHarold,\nwhat is it you wanted to discuss?$k$p$E通常,汗|If it's about $Nu again, it's fine.\nI can talk to $Nu myself...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaNo, this concerns you and I,\nnot $Nu.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|You and I?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|I am sorry for all the mistakes\nI had committed the other day.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|Again,\nyou don't need to apologize for that.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|No, that's not all. Each time I failed you,\nyou gave me your forgiveness...$k$p$Eキメ,|Such generosity is what\nhas won over my heart.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Huh?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|I know that you and I may be\ntoo far apart in standing...$k$pAnd this may not be much\nfor royalty like you, but...$k$p$E怒,照|I got this for you.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|...What a lovely ring...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaCould you please marry me?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|…………$k$pAre you sure about this ring?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Come again?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaPerhaps you had some accident on\nthe way and got the wrong one...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaNo, this is no mistake.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaAll right.$k$p$E苦,|And are you sure you\nwant to give this to me?$k$pYou haven't hit your head and mistaken\nme for someone else, have you?$k$p$E苦,汗|Here, take a good look.\nIt's me, Camilla...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,照|No, I am not mistaken on that either.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|I see...$k$p$E笑,|Haha... You do have a rather cute face.\nI never even noticed.$k$pI was always watching $Nu,\nwhen maybe...$k$pI should have paid more attention to you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,照|Then... your answer is...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Though your bad luck does\nseem quite worrisome...$k$p$E笑,|I like how earnest and faithful you are.$k$pI say that not as your liege,\nbut as a woman.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaTh-then, you will...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes, I shall.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|Thank you!$k$p$Eキメ,照|Lady Camilla! From this very moment, I,\nHarold, will protect you with my own life!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|Could you please not get so fired up?$k$pI'm worried what might\nhappen with your luck...$k
